{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#13554: defineEmits and references in the template - either misleading TS or bug.",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:16:13.851616+00:00",
  "text": "defineEmits and references in the template - either misleading TS or bug.\n\n### Vue version\n\n3.5.14\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\n\nhttps://play.vuejs.org/#\n\n#### Context\nFirstly thanks to the community and the maintainers, I really like vue.\nI was replacing my type-unsafe `$attrs.myEvent` with typesafe events defined with `defineEmits`.\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n```\n<!-- parent -->\n<script setup>\nimport Comp from './Comp.vue';\n\nfunction printToConsole(...args) {\n  console.log('waso', ...args);\n}\n</script>\n\n<template>\n  <Comp @myEmit=\"printToConsole\" />\n</template>\n\n<-- Comp.vue -->\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\ndefineEmits<{\n  (event: 'myEmit', stuff?: string): void;\n}>();\n</script>\n\n<template>\n  <!-- 1. this works if you comment out `defineEmits` -->\n  <!-- <input type=\"button\" value=\"my button\" @click=\"$attrs.onMyEmit\" /> - {{ typeof $attrs.onMyEmit }} -->\n\n  <!-- 2. this sort of looks like it should work based on the typing of `onMyEmit` but doesn't -->\n  <input type=\"button\" value=\"my button\" @click=\"onMyEmit\" /> - {{ typeof onMyEmit }}\n\n  <!-- 3. this works but is clunkier -->\n  <!-- <input type=\"button\" value=\"my button\" @click=\"(...args) => $emit('myEmit', 'hi')\" />  -->\n</template>\n```\n\nIn `Comp.vue` above, the resolved types really make it look like I could access `onMyEmit` as a function\n![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e03a8b06-feb5-4efc-abce-56a5c784c465)\n\n### What is expected?\n\nOne of two:\n1. Either the type `onMyEmit` isn't reported in the template\n2. or `onMyEmit` is indeed defined.\n\n### What is actually happening?\n\nAt runtime `onMyEmit` doesn't exist.\n\n### System Info\n\n```shell\nhttps://play.vuejs.org/#\n\nTS: 5.8.3, I am not sure what version of vue-tsc the vue playground is using.\n```\n\n### Any additional comments?\n\n_No response_",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    "scope: types"
  ],
